---
title: Montreal-Spiced Portobello Burgers with Sweet Potato Wedges
description: This portobello mushroom burger is seasoned with Montreal steak spice and topped with a cream cheese and chive stuffing. Sweet potato wedges are the perfect side for this earthy veggie dinner!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/burgers-de-portobellos-aux-epices-de-montreal-da495e35.jpg
